quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  30,1,"Alif Lām Mīm."
  30,2,"The Romans have been overcome"
  30,3,"in the nearest1land. But after having been overcome, they will overcome(their enemy)"
  30,4,"in a few1years. The command belongs to Allah, in the past and in the future. And on that day, the believers will exult"
  30,5,"in Allah’s support. He supports whomever He wills, and He is the Almighty, the Bestower of mercy."